\title{Segalification and the Boardman–Vogt tensor product}
\date{2025-12-18}
\author/literal{Shaul Barkan}
\author/literal{Jan Steinebrunner}
\meta{doi}{10.2140/agt.2025.25.5439}
\taxon{Reference}


\p{
We develop an analog of Dugger and Spivak's necklace formula providing an explicit
description of the Segal space generated by an arbitrary simplicial space. We apply
this to obtain a formula for the Segalification of #{n}-fold simplicial spaces, a new
proof of the invariance of right fibrations, and a new construction of the
Boardman–Vogt tensor product of #{\infty}-operads, for which we also derive an
explicit formula.
}

